                <p>Enhance the safety of your home with our expert residential fire door installation services. All our fire doors comply with the latest UK fire safety standards, ensuring that your property is equipped with the best protection available. Our services also include the fitting of essential safety features such as door closers and intumescent strips. These strips, crucial in fire safety, expand when exposed to heat, sealing any gaps between the door and the frame to block the spread of fire and smoke for up to 30 minutes.</p>
